{"tid":1161293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子曉麗苑停車場墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-05-19T05:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T06:14:01.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"224d8d1fa440b98d1a3eae1afb577eeb83520be9","tid":1161293,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:27:42.000Z","msg":"秀茂坪曉麗苑商場對開，早上近10時，一名男子由停車場6樓墮下，倒卧地面，傷重昏迷，警方及救護員接報到場，將男事主送院，惟經搶救後證實不治。警員在停車場6樓調查，發現相信是事主的眼鏡及手機。據了解，事主今晨曾向家人透露不開心，然後離家外出，家人遍尋不獲，稍後卻接獲警員通知方知噩耗，悲痛不已。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=56afd3b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190519/59617198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190519%2F59617198&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=944e0fa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190519%2F59617198&h=d5f08791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190519/59617198</a>"},{"pid":"ee347de972b1d96ab17440f967e4959c81fc83c7","tid":1161293,"uid":251925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:28:49.000Z","msg":"又重刷"},{"pid":"809efb9521ea994a2ab2b0c255b9204bd1bb182d","tid":1161293,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:28:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b701d6c3f9b452ad4c971aa5fd4099fc05e144d","tid":1161293,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl